---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Sources - Ferienwohnungsverein Jungfrau"
  description="All studies, official sources, and media articles underpinning our position on short-term rentals – transparent and traceable."
  langAlt="/quellen/"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section page-hero hero--intro">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Our Sources</h1>
      <p>Transparency matters to us. Here you'll find all studies, official sources, and media articles underpinning our position. Every figure on this website can be traced back to its original source here – the links lead directly to the external documents.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Studies -->
  <section class="section section--white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Key Studies and Reports</h2>
      <ul class="source-list">
        <li id="sab-airbnb">SAB (Swiss Association for Mountain Regions) – <a href="https://www.sab.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Aktuelle-Ansaetze-zur-Regulierung-von-Airbnb_Version-2.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">"Current Approaches to Regulating Airbnb in Switzerland"</a>, 25 Nov 2025</li>
        <li id="are-wirkungsanalyse">ARE / Rütter Soceco AG (commissioned by SECO) – <a href="https://www.are.admin.ch/dam/de/sd-web/qQ6V9lgU8Vs1/wirkungsanalyse-zwg-vertiefungsanalyse-volkswirtschaft.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">"Impact Analysis of the Second Homes Act"</a>, 9 Dec 2020</li>
        <li id="bfs-parahotellerie">Swiss Federal Statistical Office (BFS) – <a href="https://www.bfs.admin.ch/bfs/de/home/statistiken/tourismus/beherbergung/parahotellerie.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Parahotel Statistics</a></li>
        <li id="falk-scaglione-geneva">Martin Falk, Miriam Scaglione (2023) – "Effects of regulations on the Airbnb market in Geneva", <em>Tourism Economics</em>, 30(3)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Official sources -->
  <section class="section section--subtle">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Official Sources</h2>
      <ul class="source-list">
        <li id="are-wohnungsinventar"><a href="https://www.are.admin.ch/de/wohnungsinventar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ARE – Housing Inventory (primary and second homes)</a></li>
        <li id="are-zweitwohnungen"><a href="https://www.are.admin.ch/are/de/home/raumentwicklung-und-raumplanung/raumplanungsrecht/zweitwohnungen.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ARE – Second Homes, Spatial Planning Law</a></li>
        <li id="seco-sem-meldewesen"><a href="https://www.news.admin.ch/de/nsb?id=103780" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SECO/SEM report on accommodation registration</a> (17 Jan 2025)</li>
        <li id="be-baugesetz"><a href="https://www.belex.sites.be.ch/app/de/texts_of_law/721.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Canton Bern – Building Act BSG 721.0</a></li>
        <li id="hev-leerwohnungsziffer"><a href="https://www.hev-be.ch/vermieten/statistiken/leerwohnungsziffer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HEV Canton Bern – Vacancy Rate</a></li>
        <li id="interlaken-logiernaechte"><a href="https://www.interlaken.ch/info-und-service/ueber-interlaken-tourismus/berichte-statistiken/logiernaechtestatistiken" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Municipality of Interlaken – Overnight Stay Statistics</a></li>
        <li id="toi-jahresberichte"><a href="https://jahresbericht.interlaken.swiss/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Interlaken Tourism Organisation – Annual Reports</a></li>
        <li id="hotelleriesuisse"><a href="https://www.hotelleriesuisse.ch/de/branche-und-politik/wirtschaftspolitik/digitale-wirtschaft/sharing-economy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HotellerieSuisse – "Sharing Economy and Airbnb"</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Press -->
  <section class="section section--white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Press Articles (Selection)</h2>
      <ul class="source-list">
        <li id="bz-wilderswil"><a href="https://www.bernerzeitung.ch/wilderswil-sp-zieht-airbnb-initiative-zurueck-360616072283" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Berner Zeitung – "After the Wilderswil vote: SP withdraws Airbnb initiative"</a></li>
        <li id="bz-boenigen"><a href="https://www.bernerzeitung.ch/boenigen-gemeinde-will-airbnb-in-wohngebieten-verbieten-753348313841" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Berner Zeitung – "Bönigen wants to massively restrict Airbnb and co."</a></li>
        <li id="swissinfo-boedeli"><a href="https://www.swissinfo.ch/ger/airbnb-initiativen-auf-dem-b%C3%B6deli-bleiben-g%C3%BCltig/89948272" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">swissinfo.ch – "Airbnb initiatives on the Bödeli remain valid"</a></li>
        <li id="chamber-progress-nyc"><a href="https://medium.com/chamber-of-progress/new-nyc-data-shows-that-airbnb-restrictions-arent-solving-housing-crunch-b835803d0040" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Chamber of Progress – "New NYC Data Shows that Airbnb Restrictions Aren't Solving Housing Crunch"</a></li>
        <li id="nzz-tessin"><a href="https://www.nzz.ch/schweiz/tourismus-tessin-ferienwohnungen-duerfen-nur-noch-waehrend-90-tagen-im-jahr-vermietet-werden-ld.1739335" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">NZZ – "Tourism Ticino: Holiday apartments may only be rented for 90 days a year"</a></li>
        <li id="plattformj-boedeli"><a href="https://www.plattformj.ch/artikel/231162/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Plattform J – "SP Bödeli-Jungfrau: five municipalities, five approaches"</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="spacer-top">This list is a selection of key sources, not exhaustive. For questions about specific sources: <a href="/en/contact/">Contact</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .source-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.4rem;
  }

  .source-list li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  /* Target highlight when deep-linked from body text */
  .source-list li:target {
    background: var(--color-bg-subtle);
    box-shadow: -0.6rem 0 0 var(--color-bg-subtle), 0.6rem 0 0 var(--color-bg-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  /* Clearly mark external links as external */
  .source-list a[href^="http"]::after {
    content: " ↗";
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .spacer-top {
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
  }
</style>
